N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1273.12 - Automotive and ramp equipment refueling restricted

State Regulations

Automotive and ramp equipment shall be refueled only at
refueling stations and from dispensing devices approved by the
manager. Notes
